docs.lead_paragraph: Foreign exchanges jumped sharply higher last week with a vigor not witnessed in months. The major currencies reached their highest levels in several years, while the gold bloc in some instances ran above and in others approximated the point at which gold could be shipped abroad.

docs.snippet: Foreign exchanges were strong again last week, continuing the movement which set in several weeks ago. The upturn was a reflection of the efforts of the inflationist group in Congress to force the Treasury to issue additional amounts of currency, at...
docs.lead_paragraph: Foreign exchanges were strong again last week, continuing the movement which set in several weeks ago. The upturn was a reflection of the efforts of the inflationist group in Congress to force the Treasury to issue additional amounts of currency, at the same time blocking any effort to impose new taxes to cover bonus requirements, farm and relief demands.
